{"TopicId":100761,"ForumId":21,"TopicTitle":"Build/Showcase your pod racer for 0.90","CreatedByName":"Roflcopterkklol","CreatedById":119190,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-02-26T05:00:23Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Roflcopterkklol","CreatedById":119190,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-02-26T05:00:23Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cdiv style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\u003Cp\u003EAfter building a pod racer for 0.90 it got me wanting moar, I would love to see all the different and crazy designs people can come up with for building these.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EMake sure to provide pics/download links and let people know what mods you have used if any:wink:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003Econstruction tips: \u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003Econtrol wheels make things easier and try to avoid using any aerodynamic parts (wings/controls) they tend to mess with the thrust of jets when they pass behind them in 0.90 for some reason.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:10px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ERecommended mods: \u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EKerbal Attachment System.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022http://www.curse.com/ksp-mods/kerbal/223900-kerbal-attachment-system-kas\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttp://www.curse.com/ksp-mods/kerbal...ent-system-kas\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EKerbal foundries wheels and repolsors.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022https://kerbalstuff.com/mod/58/Kerbal_Foundries_Wheels_and_Repulsors_ALPHA\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://kerbalstuff.com/mod/58/Kerba...epulsors_ALPHA\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EAnd remember, the most important thing is that you have fun \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 alt=\u